attrs.script:
#!/bin/bash
export LC_ALL="en_US.UTF-8"
export LC_CTYPE="en_US.UTF-8"
sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get install -y python-pip python-dev python-virtualenv
### Clear old files and installation
rm -rf /home/ubuntu/.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py tensorflow
mkdir -p tensorflow
mkdir -p logs
virtualenv /home/ubuntu/tensorflow/
export LC_ALL="en_US.UTF-8"
export LC_CTYPE="en_US.UTF-8"
source /home/ubuntu/tensorflow/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install tensorflow
pip install jupyter
jupyter notebook --generate-config
sed -i -e 's/#c.NotebookApp.ip.*/c.NotebookApp.ip = \"*\"/g' /home/ubuntu/.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py
sed -i -e 's/#c.NotebookApp.password.*/c.NotebookApp.password = u\"sha1:bdb3cf1880ff:92ba74e1391bdb2171fd27e1688f45d0c19a6655\"/g' /home/ubuntu/.jupyter/jupyter_notebook_config.py
nohup bash -c  "source /home/ubuntu/tensorflow/bin/activate; /home/ubuntu/tensorflow/bin/tensorboard --logdir /home/ubuntu/logs/ --host 0.0.0.0 --port 6006 &" > /tmp/t.out
nohup bash -c  "source /home/ubuntu/tensorflow/bin/activate; /home/ubuntu/tensorflow/bin/jupyter notebook &" > /tmp/jupyter.out
#!/bin/bash
